    return `BIGBASKET GROCERY
Order #BB234567890
Date: 22/03/2026
GST: 27AABCU9603R1ZN
---
Amul Milk 1L x2              68
Onions 1kg x1                40
Tomatoes 500g x1             35
Bread Brown x1               45
